22:34.000 --> 22:38.000
And, accordingly, see who to offer your product to.

22:38.000 --> 22:42.000
Why not use the network that our competitors use?

22:42.000 --> 22:48.000
The next step we take is to analyze the offers in the regional press.

22:48.000 --> 22:54.000
