It will only be necessary to work on your product,

24:58.000 --> 25:01.000
on the specifics of your company, of your product.

25:01.000 --> 25:04.000
Thus, from a large mass of intermediaries,

25:04.000 --> 25:07.000
you choose those that are most relevant and acceptable to you.

25:07.000 --> 25:12.000
And in parallel with this step, we develop a typical contract and a discount matrix.

25:12.000 --> 25:13.000
For what?

25:13.000 --> 25:18.000
In order for the intermediaries we select to make the appropriate offer.

25:18.000 --> 25:23.000
After all, we cannot make our offer without a contract and a discount, right?

25:23.000 --> 25:27.000
Therefore, two points, the selection of intermediaries and the development of a discount matrix,

25:27.000 --> 25:30.000
and a typical contract are carried out in parallel.

25:30.000 --> 25:37.000
The next step we take is to conclude short-term contracts for the supply of our products.

25:37.000 --> 25:39.000
Why short-term?

25:39.000 --> 25:42.000
