They immediately conclude exclusive contracts,

26:00.000 --> 26:04.000
on volume, dealer contracts, then lose the market.

26:04.000 --> 26:07.000
Therefore, it is necessary to take a test step first.

26:07.000 --> 26:11.000
When we take a test step, we look at the consequences.

26:12.000 --> 26:18.000
The next step is trial deliveries and additional selection of intermediaries.

26:18.000 --> 26:20.000
We choose the best of them.

26:20.000 --> 26:22.000
We don't need many of them.

